{
  "stem": "24466.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That shows you-- I believe that I mentioned to you this-- how low the characters of people have been, of some of the high ranking police, Jewish police, went.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and if I-- I have to mention that to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other thing [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was before my escape to the partisans, to go to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have my wife to-- on the Aryan side to see that she would be safe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other thing, talking about the police, the Jewish police-- happens that every few hours, as told you, that the block are-- block was on four-- what are call it?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Guard towers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guard-- guard towers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they were-- could see that already coming, a guard is coming, to change them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was a possibility for my wife and one of the-- and the wife of the Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Riszfeld, who went also to the partisans with me together, to open the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a little opening where the-- to open them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they were going, they went-- when they could see that they are going already to change them, and so on, so they went down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was only a strip there-- there-- to let them out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the police didn't want to open the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of them tell me, if he want-- if Kaufman wants to save his wife, let them pay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that time, I paid them 70 ruble in gold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were gold--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coins.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And let out my wife that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the second time how the police, the Jewish police, were handling and were dealing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who-- who did Ala escape with-- escape with?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who was with her?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lutka.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lutka Riszfeld",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-U-T-K-A R-I-S-Z-F-E-L-D.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
